metadata.name: AlphaKicks : CryptoPunks
metadata.description:
AlphaKicks is the result of combining art and fashion within the NFT world. Handcrafted with love, in India. The design process is a collaboration between brushes and paints. All shoes are custom made upon order and are hand-painted to perfection. The designs are meant to turn heads, so expect nothing less! ;)


- Each design is painted manually.
- Created with Angelus Leather Paints.
- Every piece is "sealed" with an acrylic finisher. This will help ensure your design lasts the lifetime of the sneaker.
- Scratch proof & water resistant art.
- Crafted on 100% retail authentic sneakers of your choice.
- Processing & Shipping time is around 3-4 weeks.

For more details contact:
artable2019@gmail.com
